content:
Supported Browsers for Chat Notifications

Chat notifications help agents respond to chats efficiently by alerting agents when certain events occur. The types of chat notifications that are supported are determined by the web browsers your agents use.

Available in: Salesforce Classic, Performance Editions, Developer Edition orgs created after June 14, 2012, Unlimited Edition and Enterprise Edition with Service Cloud

The legacy chat product is scheduled for retirement on February 14, 2026.

Two types of chat notifications are available in Chat:

Chat request notifications
Disconnect notifications

Browser        Version      Audio Notifications Supported?     Desktop Notifications Supported?
Google Chrome   Most recent stable version       Yes         Yes
Mozilla Firefox  Most recent stable version       Yes         Yes
Apple Safari     6.x on Mac OS X          Yes         Yes
Windows Internet Explorer    11            Yes         No
title: Supported Browsers for Chat Notifications in Service Cloud
